{"tid":1680913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[扮撤軍？]  美國要保護庫德族控制油田 俄羅斯批國際土匪","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:38:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64085b6923480b4cf20ac4a2382f7db8a7972d56","tid":1680913,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"美國要保護庫德族控制油田 俄羅斯批國際土匪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910260214.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201910260214.aspx&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=026d334c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910260214.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社莫斯科26日綜合外電報導）俄羅斯今天譴責美國是「國際土匪」，此前美國宣布有意保護由庫德族民兵控制的敘利亞油田。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯發表批評美國的聲明之前，美國國防部長艾斯培（Mark Esper）表示，美軍正強化在敘利亞代爾祖爾省（Deir Ezzor）軍力的部署，包括機械化部隊。代爾祖爾省靠近伊拉克邊境，擁有敘利亞最大的油田。<br />\n<br />\n艾斯培出訪布魯塞爾途中告訴記者，美軍的任務是阻止伊斯蘭國（IS）進入油田，而取得「可讓他們在這個區域內發動襲擊、攻擊歐洲及美國的資源」。<br />\n<br />\n大約有200名美軍目前駐守在當地。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國防部發表聲明說：「美國目前所作所為，奪取及控制敘利亞東部的油田，簡直就是國際土匪。」<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國防部指出，所有蘊藏在敘利亞的碳氫化合物不是屬於伊斯蘭國，當然「更不屬於對抗伊斯蘭國的美國防衛者，而是專屬於敘利亞」。（譯者：曹宇帆/核稿：盧映孜）1081026"},{"pid":"f7a6e84b1c5bebc438ac636909c0f6ddb3504bf6","tid":1680913,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"31776b345557c4135cbdd17c46286b2186bae1b5","tid":1680913,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=9e10d066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cda3a043094a84c331796488b2f41d369320e83","tid":1680913,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"南Y島個頭有冇油田?"},{"pid":"de15403a2f24eb6d76e191f40e60621c14cf8083","tid":1680913,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=1c53da24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"c7212f9f60b7a080e6169b02fe6b91bbc8c2efef","tid":1680913,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入，係咪用來交換isis 情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45868ccbc4ddd37ef29d4c8a079493ec426abead","tid":1680913,"uid":189138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"香港都有油田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0